We are glad to welcome everyone who waited and followed the project! Our story began three years ago, when we successfully launched our first watch NIXOID Classic. NIXIE lamps have not been produced for over thirty years, and every year it becomes more difficult to find untouched lamps that can display the time. We searched for a long time and found an untouched warehouse of lamps from the times of the USSR, and the project became possible.The watch also received tilt sensor,more capacious battery and magnetic charging connector too. Let's further explore what new we have added during this time. We have thoroughly worked out the new case, this also influenced the size of the watch, now they have become more ergonomic. Most importantly, we have introduced the accelerometer function, now there is no need to constantly press the button. We made many prototypes and tested them for a long time.    That's not all we have improved our product in, to find out more, read on.  NIXOID the world's first Dual-core tube wristwatch.  Watch has two cores, a separate core is responsible for processing only accelerometer data. This technical solution made it possible to improve the autonomy and accuracy of the accelerometer. Materials The watch is made of durable weapon-grade aluminum alloy by milling from one piece of metal using high-precision CNC equipment.  The watch has become even thinner and lighter, only 16.9 mm thick.    The top of the watch is covered with a sapphire crystal, with a hardness of 9H. The glass has a high hardness and can`t be scratched.  At the watch will be available in 6 colors:
Deep Black;
Polished Classic;
Mars Red;
 Military Green; 
Violet;
Gold
PLAZMA Coated;
 Every watch has precision laser engraving with unique serial and backer number.  The straps are made of Fluorine rubber or Steel or Leather. They are very pleasant to the touch, strong and reliable.  There is a magnetic connector on the back cover, it is very convenient and gives magic in using the watch. The magnetic connector does not loosen over time and always looks like new.   The watch has a knurled button, that is pleasant to the touch and looks beautiful.  Tilt function   You can see the time by pressing a button or by gesture. The watch does not respond to accidental hand movements. All movements of the watch are processed by a separate core, to see the time you need to turn your wrist away from you, and then back, towards you. This gesture is programmed intentionally, and several times reduces false actuations, which has a good effect on the battery life.
The autonomy of the watch with the accelerometer on is up to 10 days in everyday use;
The autonomy of the watch with the accelerometer turned off is up to 25-30 days in everyday use;
With the accelerometer disabled, the watch can be stored for up to two months in sleep mode. 

 You will receive a special milled keychain with laser engraving to enable or disable the tilt function. You can attach it to the your keys, and it will always be with you, it's convenient! Tilt function available only in Pro version of watch!Unlocked optionsUNLOCKED:
 - High Quality Stainless Steel straps in black or silver;
 - Handmade Leather straps in red or brown or black to your taste;
 - Custom laser engraving, possible to engrave any text or picture, any idea is possible!;
  - New unique body colors, Classic Gold and Nuclear Violet are available;
  - We obtained a unique color Plasma and texture of the case without the use  paints, by means of plasma irradiation.  The case has a unique texture and color;
 - A nice bonus - accelerated delivery of your reward!;

About limit of tubesTake a look at this box. This box has not been opened for 25 years. These are untouched IN-16 lamps, which were stored in a closed military warehouse. It is a complete success to find several boxes of these lamps in 2022. There are not many Nixie lamps left in the world, perhaps the one of last boxes.Don't miss this chance to get yourself a piece of the story.If you support us!  We have shown everything on the schedule for the fulfillment of all orders, we are also ready for amendments, so we purchased all the parts in advance. We are always in touch with you. Our partners from Ukraine have extensive experience in launching and coordinating projects in the field of crowdfunding. Rewards Tribute to the Nixoid Classic Without knowing history it is impossible to create the future. You can also get the Classic version of the Nixoid for the collection if you like. The quantity is limited to 50 pieces. Only a black version of the watch with a black strap is available. We will add this product to the rewards and will be available separately.____LinksCustomers love our watches! Risks and challengesDear supporters, we hasten to assure you that we are all ready to start the project. We have behind us the experience of successful campaigns, and most importantly, we really value our reputation. We guarantee you fast delivery and will try to answer all your questions within 24 hours.
